WEBVTT

00:02.167 --> 00:05.833
by
HOME BOX OFFICE

00:05.867 --> 00:09.833
A Division of TIME WARNER
ENTERTAINMENT COMPANY, L.P.

00:27.033 --> 00:29.300
OH, SO...

00:29.333 --> 00:32.067
HOW ARE WE DOING ?

00:32.100 --> 00:33.533
ALRIGHT.

00:33.567 --> 00:34.533
FEELING ALRIGHT,

00:34.567 --> 00:35.700
NO UNCOMFORTABLE
SENSATIONS ?

00:35.733 --> 00:36.833
NO, HOW MUCH LONGER ?

00:36.867 --> 00:38.633
UH, MAYBE 10
TO 15 MORE MINUTES.

00:38.667 --> 00:40.367
AH, VERY GOOD,
VERY GOOD.

00:40.400 --> 00:43.700
YEAH, I THINK YOU'LL BE VERY
HAPPY WITH THE TREATMENT.

00:43.733 --> 00:45.567
MM-HMM.
REALLY ?

00:45.600 --> 00:47.567
YOU ACTUALLY YOU THINK
YOU'RE GONNA FIX MY NECK, HUH ?

00:47.600 --> 00:49.800
WELL, OF COURSE,
I ABSOLUTELY GUARANTEE IT

00:49.833 --> 00:51.933
IF YOU FOLLOW
MY PRESCRIBED COURSE.

00:51.967 --> 00:53.033
UH-HUH.

00:53.067 --> 00:54.500
FOUR TO SIX WEEKS,
MAYBE TWICE A WEEK.

00:54.533 --> 00:55.733
MM-HMM.
YEAH.

00:55.767 --> 00:57.400
WELL, FORGIVE ME FOR
SOUNDING A LITTLE CYNICAL,

00:57.433 --> 00:59.067
BUT I'VE HEARD
THAT BEFORE.

00:59.100 --> 01:00.667
YOU HAVE ?

01:00.700 --> 01:02.367
OH, YEAH, I'VE BEEN TO
A LOT OF DIFFERENT PEOPLE.

01:02.400 --> 01:04.267
THEY ALL KIND OF
TELL ME THE SAME THING.

01:04.300 --> 01:05.133
REALLY ?

01:05.167 --> 01:06.200
I NEVER GET
ANY RESULTS.

01:06.233 --> 01:08.567
I'VE BEEN TO DOCTORS
AND CHIROPRACTORS AND...

01:08.600 --> 01:11.467
HEALERS, PEOPLE WHO
CALL THEMSELVES HEALERS.

01:11.500 --> 01:12.333
( laughing )

01:12.367 --> 01:13.467
YEAH, HEALERS.

01:13.500 --> 01:14.400
WHAT A JOKE
THAT IS.

01:14.433 --> 01:16.333
WELL, I UNDERSTAND
YOUR CONCERNS.

01:16.367 --> 01:18.800
BUT ACUPUNCTURE HAS BEEN
AROUND FOR A LONG TIME

01:18.833 --> 01:21.100
AND IT'S BEEN IN MY FAMILY
FOR SEVERAL HUNDRED YEARS.

01:21.133 --> 01:22.100
YEAH ?

01:22.133 --> 01:23.100
YES.

01:23.133 --> 01:24.100
UH-HUH.

01:24.133 --> 01:25.767
I ABSOLUTELY GUARANTEE
TOTAL RECOVERY.

01:25.800 --> 01:26.800
YOU DO, HUH ?

01:26.833 --> 01:27.700
YES.

01:27.733 --> 01:28.733
OKAY, I'LL TELL
YOU WHAT.

01:28.767 --> 01:30.100
I GOT A LITTLE
PROPOSITION FOR YOU.

01:30.133 --> 01:31.333
HMM ?

01:31.367 --> 01:34.400
IF YOU CAN FIX MY NECK,
I'LL GIVE YOU $5,000.

01:34.433 --> 01:36.067
AND IF YOU CAN'T,

01:36.067 --> 01:38.267
THEN I DON'T PAY FOR
ANY OF THE TREATMENTS.

01:38.300 --> 01:39.667
$5,000 ?

01:39.700 --> 01:40.933
$5,000.

01:40.967 --> 01:43.067
IF I TREAT YOU
AND YOU RECOVER ?

01:43.067 --> 01:44.067
YEP.

01:44.100 --> 01:46.067
AND IF YOU DO NOT RECOVER,
I GET NOTHING ?

01:46.067 --> 01:47.267
YOU GET NOTHING.

01:47.300 --> 01:49.433
WELL, IT WOULD BE LIKE TAKING
CANDY FROM A BABY, BUT--

01:49.467 --> 01:50.433
REALLY ?

01:50.467 --> 01:51.267
YES.

01:51.300 --> 01:53.300
I LOVE
YOUR CONFIDENCE.

01:53.333 --> 01:55.267
WELL, WAIT A MINUTE NOW,
IF I CURE YOU,

01:55.300 --> 01:57.700
HOW WOULD I KNOW IF
YOU ARE CURED OR NOT ?

01:57.733 --> 01:59.767
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING ?

01:59.800 --> 02:01.700
YOU'RE SAYING THAT
I WOULDN'T TELL YOU ?

02:01.733 --> 02:03.967
JUST SO I WOULDN'T HAVE TO PAY
THE MONEY, THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

02:04.067 --> 02:06.167
COME ON,
I'M A MAN OF HONOR.

02:06.200 --> 02:08.067
IT'S A FAMILY
TRADITION, HONOR.

02:08.067 --> 02:09.367
WELL, IT'S NOT
IN MY FAMILY,

02:09.400 --> 02:12.067
BUT I'M TRYING
TO BREAK THE MOLD.

02:12.100 --> 02:13.467
ALRIGHT, DONE.

02:13.500 --> 02:16.267
I HOPE YOU WIN.

02:26.267 --> 02:27.600
LARRY ?

02:27.633 --> 02:29.967
( female )
THANK YOU.

02:31.167 --> 02:32.200
WHOA.

02:37.900 --> 02:39.100
HOW YOU DOIN' ?

02:39.133 --> 02:40.833
HEY.

02:40.867 --> 02:43.667
IT'S BARRY.

02:43.700 --> 02:44.933
YEAH.

02:48.100 --> 02:49.133
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
LOOK AT ME THAT WAY,

02:49.167 --> 02:50.633
NO NEED FOR PITY.

02:50.667 --> 02:53.800
NO, I MEAN, I'M JUST
SHOCKED TO SEE YOU HERE...

02:53.833 --> 02:56.167
WORKING.

02:56.200 --> 02:58.067
HOW LONG YOU
BEEN DOING THIS ?

02:58.067 --> 02:59.600
IT'S BEEN AWHILE.

02:59.633 --> 03:01.833
WHAT DO YOU WANT ?

03:02.800 --> 03:04.367
UM...

03:04.400 --> 03:07.767
QUARTER POUND OF SWISS
AND A HALF POUND OF TURKEY.

03:07.800 --> 03:09.333
QUARTER POUND
OF SWISS...

03:09.367 --> 03:10.233
( together )
AND A HALF
POUND OF TURKEY.

03:10.267 --> 03:12.067
ALRIGHT.

03:12.067 --> 03:14.933
DO YOU EVER HEAR FROM
ANY OF THOSE OLD GUYS
AT "SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE" ?

03:14.967 --> 03:18.067
UH, YOU KNOW, SOMETIMES YOU
RUN INTO SOMEBODY, YOU KNOW ?

03:18.067 --> 03:20.400
I TALK TO ELLIOT
AND ANDY OCCASIONALLY.

03:20.433 --> 03:21.633
OH, YEAH,
HOW'S ELLIOT DOING ?

03:21.667 --> 03:22.667
GOOD.

03:22.700 --> 03:25.900
THE WRITING WASN'T
HAPPENING, HUH ?

03:25.933 --> 03:29.200
WELL, YOU KNOW, JUST COULDN'T
WRITE FOR TV ANYMORE.

03:29.233 --> 03:31.433
THINGS ARE GOING GOOD.

03:31.467 --> 03:33.067
EXCEPT FOR THIS THING
WITH MY DAD...

03:33.067 --> 03:34.067
SITUATION.

03:34.100 --> 03:35.467
YOU REMEMBER
MY DAD ?

03:35.500 --> 03:36.600
YEAH.

03:36.633 --> 03:39.600
HE CAME TO YOUR HOUSE,
YEAH, I REMEMBER.

03:39.633 --> 03:41.633
HE'S DOING THIS LIKE...

03:41.667 --> 03:43.267
( coughing )

03:43.300 --> 03:44.400
THIS WEIRD
NUMBER ON ME--

03:44.433 --> 03:47.367
TRY AND PUT THAT
ON THE SWISS IF YOU CAN.

03:47.400 --> 03:48.333
I COVERED MY MOUTH.

03:48.367 --> 03:49.267
YEAH, SURE.

03:49.300 --> 03:51.333
YEAH, SO, MY DAD
IS JUST DOING THIS,

03:51.367 --> 03:53.600
HE'S BASICALLY DYING
IS WHAT'S HAPPENING.

03:53.633 --> 03:57.167
AND HE HAD
A TRIPLE BYPASS,

03:57.200 --> 03:58.533
A QUADRUPLE BYPASS.

03:58.567 --> 04:01.567
OH, BOY, HE'S GOT SEVEN
TOTAL BASES THERE, YEAH.

04:01.600 --> 04:03.933
AND UH, HE'S LEFT ME
THE MONEY IN HIS WILL.

04:03.967 --> 04:06.067
BUT HE WON'T LET ME
HAVE ANY OF IT, YOU KNOW ?

04:06.067 --> 04:09.467
NOT A PENNY, UNTIL, LIKE,
HE'S ACTUALLY DEAD.

04:09.500 --> 04:11.900
YOUR FATHER'S GOT A LOT
OF MONEY, DOESN'T HE ?

04:11.933 --> 04:13.900
YEAH, YEAH, YOU KNOW,
AND SO, IT'S, UH...

04:13.933 --> 04:15.467
HE KNOWS YOU'RE
WORKING IN A DELI ?

04:15.500 --> 04:16.733
OF COURSE
HE DOES, YEAH.

04:16.767 --> 04:19.067
AND HE WON'T GIVE YOU
THE MONEY UNTIL HE DIES ?

04:19.100 --> 04:20.367
WHY DO PEOPLE
DO THAT ?

04:20.400 --> 04:22.733
I DON'T KNOW WHY YOU HAVE
TO WAIT UNTIL HE DIES.

04:22.767 --> 04:23.933
THAT'S CRAZY.

04:23.967 --> 04:26.567
YOU'D THINK THAT HE WOULD
WANT HIS KID TO BE HAPPY,

04:26.600 --> 04:28.600
LIKE, FOR, AS HIS LAST
MEMORIES OF HIM, YOU KNOW ?

04:28.633 --> 04:30.400
ARE YOU GUYS OUT OF
PEANUT BUTTER HERE

04:30.433 --> 04:31.967
'CAUSE I CAN'T
FIND IT.

04:32.067 --> 04:34.600
UM, HEY, LET ME
ASK YOU SOMETHING.

04:34.633 --> 04:38.200
IT'S REALLY AMAZING THAT
YOU CAME IN HERE TODAY.

04:38.233 --> 04:39.467
IT COULD REALLY
HELP ME OUT.

04:39.500 --> 04:40.367
RIGHT.

04:40.400 --> 04:42.700
I NEED TO
BORROW $5,000.

04:42.733 --> 04:45.867
OF COURSE YOU DO.

04:45.900 --> 04:48.300
I'LL BE ABLE TO PAY YOU BACK
AS SOON AS HE, YOU KNOW,

04:48.333 --> 04:49.467
AS HE GOES.

04:49.500 --> 04:51.833
YEAH, WHEN DO EXPECT
THAT'LL BE ?

04:51.867 --> 04:53.100
VERY SOON...

04:53.133 --> 04:55.267
VERY SOON.

04:55.300 --> 04:57.933
OKAY, TELL ME IF
I GOT THIS RIGHT.

04:57.967 --> 04:59.500
YOU GAVE $5,000 TO
THE ACUPUNCTURIST ?

04:59.533 --> 05:00.600
YEAH.

05:00.633 --> 05:02.767
AND $5,000 TO THAT
ASSHOLE, BARRY WEINER ?

05:02.800 --> 05:04.167
OH, ASSHOLE.

05:04.200 --> 05:05.400
UMM...

05:05.433 --> 05:09.733
SO, IN THE LAST THREE HOURS
YOU'VE GIVEN AWAY $10,000.

05:11.600 --> 05:13.733
YEAH, IT'S NOT
QUITE ACCURATE.

05:13.767 --> 05:14.933
I HAVEN'T GIVEN
THE ACUPUNCTURIST

05:14.967 --> 05:16.133
THE $5,000 YET.

05:16.167 --> 05:17.800
HE HAS TO CURE MY NECK
AND I'LL BE HAPPY TO

05:17.833 --> 05:19.233
GIVE IT TO HIM IF
HE DOES, BY THE WAY.

05:19.267 --> 05:20.833
AND...

05:20.867 --> 05:22.933
WEINER'S FATHER
HAS A HEART CONDITION

05:22.967 --> 05:24.233
AND HE'S NOT SUPPOSED
TO LIVE THAT LONG,

05:24.267 --> 05:25.767
AND THEN HE'LL GIVE ME
THE MONEY BACK.

05:25.800 --> 05:28.567
AND I DON'T KNOW WHY
YOU CALL HIM AN ASSHOLE.

05:28.600 --> 05:30.500
HE'S NOT AN ASSHOLE,
HE'S JUST SHY.

05:30.533 --> 05:31.900
NO, HE'S NOT SHY.

05:31.933 --> 05:33.800
