THAN EVERYBODY ELSE,

05:33.833 --> 05:35.533
AND HE SITS THERE
AND HE JUDGES AND HE--

05:35.567 --> 05:37.400
NO, HE DOESN'T,
HE'S JUST SHY.

05:37.433 --> 05:39.900
YOU GOT SHY ASSHOLE CONFUSION,
MY FRIEND.

05:39.933 --> 05:41.233
NO, I DON'T THINK SO,
MY FRIEND.

05:41.267 --> 05:42.567
YES, I THINK SO,
MY FRIEND.

05:42.600 --> 05:44.900
PEOPLE COME TO YOU WITH THEIR
HANDS OUT, YOU CAN'T SAY NO ?

05:44.933 --> 05:47.500
I HAVE TROUBLE
SAYING NO.

05:47.533 --> 05:48.500
YOU KNOW WHY ?

05:48.533 --> 05:49.500
( knocking )

05:49.533 --> 05:50.900
'CAUSE YOU'RE
A PUSSY.

05:50.933 --> 05:52.267
I'M BEING FRANK.

05:52.300 --> 05:53.500
MAYBE I'M NICE.

05:53.533 --> 05:55.500
YOU HAVE NICE
PUSSY CONFUSION.

05:55.533 --> 05:56.867
MAYBE I'M JUST NICE.

05:56.900 --> 06:01.467
AND HE INVITED US TO HIS
WIFE'S SURPRISE BIRTHDAY PARTY

06:01.500 --> 06:03.567
AND I COULDN'T SAY
NO TO THAT EITHER.

06:03.600 --> 06:06.200
HEY THERE,
FLOWERS FOR LARRY DAVID.

06:07.633 --> 06:10.700
CHERYL, SOMEBODY
SENT ME FLOWERS.

06:10.733 --> 06:12.233
ARE THOSE FROM
YOUR MISTRESS

06:12.267 --> 06:13.333
AND YOU JUST HAVEN'T
TOLD ME ABOUT THAT ?

06:13.367 --> 06:14.367
YEAH, I WISH.

06:14.400 --> 06:15.633
THANKS.

06:15.667 --> 06:18.067
DID YOU GIVE HIM
A $5,000 TIP ?

06:18.067 --> 06:21.367
THIS IS REALLY
BIZARRE.

06:22.567 --> 06:23.533
FLOWERS.

06:23.567 --> 06:25.533
WHO WOULD
SEND YOU FLOWERS ?

06:25.567 --> 06:27.500
I DON'T KNOW.

06:27.533 --> 06:28.833
THEY'RE PRETTY.

06:28.867 --> 06:33.067
"ENJOY THESE BEAUTIFUL
ORCHIDS, KAZU."

06:33.067 --> 06:34.733
WHO'S KAZU ?

06:34.767 --> 06:37.267
THE ACUPUNCTURIST.

06:38.933 --> 06:40.733
( laughing )

06:40.767 --> 06:44.467
WHY IS THE ACUPUNCTURIST
GIVING YOU FLOWERS ?

06:46.167 --> 06:47.800
I DON'T KNOW.

06:52.233 --> 06:53.400
SO, I DON'T KNOW, YOU KNOW,
WORKING IN THE DELI,

06:53.433 --> 06:54.533
IT WAS JUST,

06:54.567 --> 06:56.800
IT WAS DEPRESSING
TO SEE HIM LIKE THAT.

06:56.833 --> 06:59.233
DID YOU EVEN KNOW, DID YOU
KNOW HE WAS WORKING THERE ?

06:59.267 --> 07:01.567
NO, I DIDN'T KNOW HE WAS
WORKING IN THE DELI.

07:01.600 --> 07:02.800
HE KEEPS IN
CONTACT WITH ME.

07:02.833 --> 07:04.433
BUT HE DIDN'T LET ME
KNOW THAT STUFF.

07:04.467 --> 07:05.567
UH-HUH, BOY.

07:05.600 --> 07:08.067
BUT FOR THE GRACE OF GOD,
GO YOU.

07:08.067 --> 07:09.300
GO ME, NOT YOU ?

07:09.333 --> 07:10.700
NO, NOT ME.

07:10.733 --> 07:12.367
YEAH, GO ME.

07:12.400 --> 07:15.533
HE INVITED ME TO
A SURPRISE PARTY...

07:15.567 --> 07:16.933
NEXT THURSDAY NIGHT
FOR HIS WIFE.

07:16.967 --> 07:17.967
YOU'RE GOING ?

07:18.067 --> 07:19.333
YEAH, I'LL PICK YOU UP,
WE'LL GO TOGETHER.

07:19.367 --> 07:22.567
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK OF
THIS WHOLE ORCHID THING ?

07:22.600 --> 07:24.367
IT'S, YOU KNOW, I THINK
IT'S SOME SORT OF

07:24.400 --> 07:25.800
JAPANESE, GAY THING.

07:25.833 --> 07:26.800
REALLY ?
YEAH.

07:26.833 --> 07:28.800
THIS IS A LITTLE STRANGE,

07:28.833 --> 07:30.133
I DON'T KNOW IF
I'LL EVEN GO BACK TO HIM.

07:30.167 --> 07:31.933
I DON'T THINK I'LL GO BACK,
'CAUSE OF TH.

07:31.967 --> 07:33.533
WOULD YOU ?
I DON'T KNOW ?

07:33.567 --> 07:34.333
WOULD YOU GO BACK ?

07:34.367 --> 07:35.967
IT'S A WEIRD THING.

07:36.067 --> 07:37.167
