07:37.200 --> 07:40.200
LET ME ASK YOU
A QUESTION.

07:40.233 --> 07:44.433
IS IT COMMON IN JAPAN FOR A MAN
TO SEND ANOTHER MAN ORCHIDS,

07:44.467 --> 07:46.600
A PROFESSIONAL MAN ?

07:48.067 --> 07:50.567
DOCTOR, OR A...

