OPEN UP A CAN OF WORMS

07:56.100 --> 07:57.367
JUST BY STARTING
TO ASK HIM.

07:57.400 --> 07:58.300
HE'S BEEN
WEIRD ALL LUNCH.

07:58.333 --> 07:59.300
WHAT THE HELL ?

07:59.333 --> 08:01.367
WHAT WAS THAT ?

08:01.400 --> 08:02.267
THAT GUY'S A FREAK.

08:02.300 --> 08:03.833
I THINK I STRUCK
A CHORD.

08:03.867 --> 08:04.867
HEY, LARRY.

08:04.900 --> 08:06.433
HEY, JOEL.

08:06.467 --> 08:08.167
GOOD TO SEE YOU.

08:08.200 --> 08:09.133
IT'S BEEN A FEW DAYS.

08:09.167 --> 08:11.167
YEAH, THIS IS
MY MANAGER, JEFF GREENE.

08:11.200 --> 08:12.500
JEFF, NICE
TO MEET YOU.

08:12.533 --> 08:14.133
HEARD A LOT
ABOUT YOU.

08:14.167 --> 08:16.133
