MY ESTATE WHEN I DIE

08:16.167 --> 08:17.400
AND I LEAVE YOU
ALL MY MONEY.

08:17.433 --> 08:19.233
HAVE YOU WORKED IT
OUT THAT WAY ?

08:19.267 --> 08:20.500
CHERYL WILL
LOVE ME.

08:20.533 --> 08:21.967
YEAH, WHAT ARE YOU DOING,
YOU'RE NOT WORKING TODAY ?

08:22.067 --> 08:23.600
YEAH, I'M GOING
BACK RIGHT NOW.

08:23.633 --> 08:24.467
