THIS CASUAL.

08:27.967 --> 08:29.500
WHAT ARE YOU,
MY MOTHER ?

08:29.533 --> 08:31.067
YOU'RE ENCROACHING
IN MY TERRITORY.

08:31.067 --> 08:34.833
I WANT YOU PEOPLE TO BE
UNCOMFORTABLE ALL THE TIME.

08:34.867 --> 08:36.067
WELL, YOU DON'T
LIKE THIS,

08:36.100 --> 08:37.900
YOU SHOULD COME BY
ON NAKED TUESDAYS.

08:37.933 --> 08:40.267
YEAH, NAKED TUESDAYS.

08:40.300 --> 08:41.800
SEE, HE'S A FUNNY LAWYER.

08:41.833 --> 08:42.733
ALRIGHT, LISTEN,
I GOTTA GO.

08:42.767 --> 08:43.833
NICE TO MEET YOU.

08:43.867 --> 08:45.233
ALRIGHT,
I'LL SEE YOU.

08:45.267 --> 08:46.300
I'LL SEE YOU
TUESDAY.

08:46.333 --> 08:48.200
CASUAL FRIDAY.

08:48.233 --> 08:49.600
PISSES ME OFF.

08:49.633 --> 08:53.967
I'M TELLING YA, SOON IT'S
GOING TO BE CASUAL MONDAY.

08:54.067 --> 08:55.333
FIVE TO 10 YEARS.

08:55.367 --> 08:57.267
THAT'S THE DIRECTION
WE'RE HEADING.

08:57.300 --> 08:59.067
IT'S GOING TO BE
A SAD STATE OF AFFAIRS.

08:59.100 --> 09:02.633
PEOPLE LIKE YOU, WALKING
AROUND LIKE PEOPLE LIKE ME.

09:02.667 --> 09:03.667
IT'S NO GOOD.

09:03.700 --> 09:04.733
I'LL NEVER DO IT.

