OKAY.

09:28.433 --> 09:29.600
OH, MY GOD.

09:29.633 --> 09:31.133
OH, JESUS !

09:36.667 --> 09:39.367
( speaking Japanese )

09:43.767 --> 09:45.967
( Japanese )

