HONEY ?

09:52.067 --> 09:53.067
WHAT ?

09:53.100 --> 09:54.100
WHERE'S JEFF ?

09:54.133 --> 09:55.133
I DON'T KNOW.

09:55.167 --> 09:56.633
HE WAS SUPPOSED TO BE
HERE 15 MINUTES AGO.

09:56.667 --> 09:57.633
I KNOW.

09:57.667 --> 09:59.333
WHY ARE WE EVEN RIDING
WITH HIM ANYWAY ?

09:59.367 --> 10:01.667
I DON'T KNOW, HE ASKED ME
IF HE COULD PICK US UP.

10:01.700 --> 10:03.133
AND YOU COULDN'T
SAY NO.

10:03.167 --> 10:04.633
LISTEN, I THINK WE SHOULD
JUST GO WITHOUT HIM.

10:04.667 --> 10:06.333
WELL, HE'LL,
I'M SURE--

10:06.367 --> 10:07.367
( knocking )

10:07.400 --> 10:08.367
OH, THERE HE IS.

10:08.400 --> 10:09.367
THERE HE IS.

10:09.400 --> 10:10.367
OKAY, LET'S
GET GOING.

10:10.400 --> 10:13.000
HI, OH,
THANK YOU.

10:13.033 --> 10:14.067
LOOK HOW
PRETTY YOU LOOK.

10:14.100 --> 10:15.000
WELL, THANK YOU.

10:15.033 --> 10:16.767
YOU LOOK PRETTY TOO.

10:16.800 --> 10:19.200
I'M A PRETTY
LITTLE GIRL.

10:19.233 --> 10:20.367
LARRY !

10:20.400 --> 10:21.767
HEY.

10:21.800 --> 10:23.267
WELL, WHAT, WHAT,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?

10:23.300 --> 10:24.267
